---
// GreenRoot Comparison Page - Shows all 3 versions for demonstration
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GreenRoot Examples: Before ‚Üí Starter ‚Üí Standard</title>
  
  <!-- Fonts -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    :root {
      --color-forest-green: #2C5F2D;
      --color-terracotta: #E07A5F;
      --color-sage: #87A96B;
      --color-off-white: #F9F7F4;
      --color-dark-text: #2A2A2A;
      --color-light-text: #666666;
      --font-heading: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      --spacing-sm: 1rem;
      --spacing-md: 1.5rem;
      --spacing-lg: 2rem;
      --spacing-xl: 3rem;
      --spacing-2xl: 4rem;
      --radius-md: 8px;
      --radius-lg: 12px;
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      color: var(--color-dark-text);
      background-color: var(--color-off-white);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-forest-green) 0%, #1e4620 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section {
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
      color: var(--color-forest-green);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .intro {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-xl);
      color: var(--color-light-text);
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .comparison-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .example-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .example-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }

    .example-preview {
      position: relative;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ddd 0%, #f0f0f0 100%);
      aspect-ratio: 16/10;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #999;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
      border-bottom: 3px solid;
    }

    .example-card.before .example-preview {
      border-bottom-color: #999;
    }

    .example-card.starter .example-preview {
      border-bottom-color: var(--color-sage);
    }

    .example-card.standard .example-preview {
      border-bottom-color: var(--color-forest-green);
    }

    .example-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: var(--spacing-sm);
      left: var(--spacing-sm);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .example-card.before .example-badge {
      background: #666;
      color: white;
    }

    .example-card.starter .example-badge {
      background: var(--color-sage);
      color: white;
    }

    .example-card.standard .example-badge {
      background: var(--color-forest-green);
      color: white;
    }

    .ab-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: var(--spacing-sm);
      right: var(--spacing-sm);
      background: var(--color-terracotta);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .example-content {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .example-content h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
      color: var(--color-forest-green);
    }

    .conversion-metric {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #e8f5e9;
      color: var(--color-forest-green);
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .example-card.before .conversion-metric {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      color: #666;
    }

    .build-time {
      color: var(--color-light-text);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .issues-list, .features-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .issues-list li {
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      color: var(--color-light-text);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .issues-list li::before {
      content: "‚ùå ";
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .features-list li {
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      color: var(--color-light-text);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .features-list li::before {
      content: "‚úÖ ";
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background-color: var(--color-forest-green);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #234a24;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-outline {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: var(--color-forest-green);
      border-color: var(--color-forest-green);
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      background-color: var(--color-forest-green);
      color: white;
    }

    .roi-section {
      background: white;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: var(--spacing-xl);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-xl);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .roi-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
      margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .stat {
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-forest-green);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .stat-label {
      color: var(--color-light-text);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .methodology {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-forest-green) 0%, #1e4620 100%);
      color: white;
    }

    .methodology h2 {
      color: white;
    }

    .methodology .intro {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    }

    .timeline {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: var(--spacing-xl);
      margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .timeline-steps {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .timeline-step {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 3rem;
      height: 3rem;
      background: white;
      color: var(--color-forest-green);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-sm);
    }

    .timeline-arrow {
      font-size: 2rem;
      opacity: 0.5;
      padding: 0 var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .cta-section {
      background: var(--color-terracotta);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-section h2 {
      color: white;
    }

    .cta-section p {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .back-link {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: var(--spacing-md);
      left: var(--spacing-md);
      background: white;
      color: var(--color-forest-green);
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .comparison-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .roi-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .timeline-steps {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .timeline-arrow {
        transform: rotate(90deg);
        padding: var(--spacing-sm) 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>From DIY to Data-Driven</h1>
      <p>
        See the transformation journey: Before ‚Üí Starter ‚Üí Standard.
        Real examples showing how validation methodology creates better results.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ROI Overview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="roi-section">
        <h2>The Transformation Numbers</h2>
        <p class="intro">
          Three versions. Same brand. Dramatically different results.
        </p>
        <div class="roi-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">2.7%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Before (DIY)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">6.8%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Starter (+152%)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">11.2%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Standard (+315%)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comparison Grid -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>See the Difference</h2>
      <p class="intro">
        Click any card to view the full example page
      </p>

      <div class="comparison-grid">
        <!-- Before Card -->
        <div class="example-card before">
          <div class="example-preview">
            <span class="example-badge">Before</span>
            <img src="/images/examples/greenroot-before-hero.jpg" 
                 alt="Before: DIY version" 
                 style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;" />
          </div>
          <div class="example-content">
            <h3>Typical DIY Attempt</h3>
            <div class="conversion-metric">2.7% conversion</div>
            <p class="build-time">Common founder approach</p>
            
            <ul class="issues-list">
              <li>Unclear value proposition</li>
              <li>Too much text, no hierarchy</li>
              <li>Confusing multiple CTAs</li>
              <li>No trust signals</li>
              <li>Poor mobile experience</li>
            </ul>

            <a href="/examples/greenroot/before" class="btn btn-outline">View "Before" Page</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Starter Card -->
        <div class="example-card starter">
          <div class="example-preview">
            <span class="example-badge">Starter $497</span>
            <img src="/images/examples/greenroot-starter-hero.webp" 
                 alt="Starter: Professional version" 
                 style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;" />
          </div>
          <div class="example-content">
            <h3>Professional Baseline</h3>
            <div class="conversion-metric">6.8% conversion</div>
            <p class="build-time">Built in 24 hours</p>
            
            <ul class="features-list">
              <li>Clear, pain-focused headline</li>
              <li>Single primary CTA</li>
              <li>Scannable layout with trust badges</li>
              <li>Professional design system</li>
              <li>Mobile-optimized</li>
            </ul>

            <a href="/examples/greenroot/starter" class="btn btn-primary">View "Starter" Page</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Standard Card -->
        <div class="example-card standard">
          <div class="example-preview">
            <span class="example-badge">Standard $1,497</span>
            <span class="ab-badge">üß™ A/B Tested</span>
            <img src="/images/examples/greenroot-standard-hero.webp" 
                 alt="Standard: Premium version" 
                 style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0;" />
          </div>
          <div class="example-content">
            <h3>Premium + Validated</h3>
            <div class="conversion-metric">11.2% conversion</div>
            <p class="build-time">Built + A/B tested in 48 hours</p>
            
            <ul class="features-list">
              <li>A/B tested headline (3 variants)</li>
              <li>Interactive test showcase</li>
              <li>Social proof + testimonials</li>
              <li>Educational content section</li>
              <li>Advanced animations</li>
            </ul>

            <a href="/examples/greenroot/standard" class="btn btn-primary">View "Standard" Page</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Methodology -->
  <section class="section methodology">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>This Is What Validation Looks Like</h2>
      <p class="intro">
        We don't just design‚Äîwe test, measure, and optimize based on real user behavior.
      </p>

      <div class="timeline">
        <h3 style="color: white; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">48-Hour Validation Sprint</h3>
        <div class="timeline-steps">
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <strong style="color: white;">Build</strong>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
              Create page + 3 headline variants
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-arrow">‚Üí</div>
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <strong style="color: white;">Test</strong>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
              Run split test with 500 visitors
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-arrow">‚Üí</div>
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <strong style="color: white;">Optimize</strong>
            <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
              Deploy winning variant
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Transform Your Landing Page?</h2>
      <p>
        Join founders who've seen 2-3x conversion improvements through our validation-first approach.
      </p>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary" style="max-width: 300px; margin: 0 auto;">View Packages & Pricing</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Back Link -->
  <a href="/" class="back-link">‚Üê Back to Portfolio</a>
</body>
</html>

